{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fc31c0d9c2","title":"给诗刊的一封信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ec84f6cd2","index":0,"year":1957,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1c864c29ee","type":"title","text":"给诗刊的一封信","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8389421862","type":"paragraph","text":"××同志和各位同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dc7e78ff0","type":"paragraph","text":"慧书早已收到，迟复为歉！遵嘱将记得起来的旧体诗词，连同你们寄来的八首，一共十八首，抄寄如另纸，请加审处。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"217f438d2b","type":"paragraph","text":"这些东西，我历来不愿意正式发表，因为是旧体，怕谬种流传，遗误青年；再则诗味不多，没有什么特色。既然你们以为可以刊载，又可为已经传抄的几首改正错字，那么，就照你们的意见办吧。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2adea1a165","type":"paragraph","text":"诗刊出版，很好，祝它成长发展。诗当然应以新诗为主体，旧诗可以写一些，但是不宜在青年中提倡，因为这种体裁束缚思想，又不易学。这些话仅供你们参考。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"adea6875af","type":"paragraph","text":"同志的敬礼，","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2333c11851","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef39e92b6b","type":"subdate","text":"一九五七年一月十二日","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"fc31c0d9c2","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":243,"end":243}}}},"__N_SSG":true}